I do think this will be the last version of this map, there aren't many changes or fixes in this version.
changes
- the sharks size, speed, and damage - the floor texture - the lighting - i added more of a trim to the wood - i have added a few more props here and there - i change the one rock on the beach (for some it works for others id was pink and black so i got rid of it) - i changed the floating light in t spawn - you can now climb aboard both the fishing boats any problems let me know
